@startuml seq-12-ask-rag-sse
title POST /search/ask — hybrid RAG + SSE stream

actor "User" as U <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n/search" as API <<service>>
participant "authenticateToken +\naskRateLimiter +\nrequireDocLibrary +\nrequireUseAi" as MW <<service>>
participant "queryOptimizer" as QO <<service>>
participant "Gemini\n(embed + rerank + stream)" as G <<external>>
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

B -> API: POST /search/ask\n{ question, chunkLimit?, history? }

API -> MW: pre-checks
alt Fail auth / rate / restrictions / validation
  API --> B: 4xx JSON (not SSE)
else Accepted
  API -> QO: optimizeQuery(question)
  QO --> API: rewrittenQuery, keywords,\ntopic, subQueries, multiHop…

  API -> G: embedQuery(rewrittenQuery)
  G --> API: embedding vector

  par
    API -> DB: vectorSearch(vecLiteral, …)
    DB --> API: vectorRows
  else
    API -> DB: runBM25Search(original Q, keywords, …)
    DB --> API: bm25Rows
  end

  API -> API: reciprocalRankFusion\n+ optional multi-hop vector passes
  API -> API: filter by RELEVANCE_LOW
  API -> G: rerankChunks(question, chunks, meta)
  G --> API: reranked → topChunks (≤6)
  API -> API: assessConfidence(topChunks)\nbuild **sources** payload

  API -> API: set SSE headers\n(text/event-stream)
  API --> B: event: **sources** + confidence

  opt findNegativeFeedbackLessons
    API -> DB: read recent negative feedback
    API -> API: buildFeedbackAddendum
  end

  loop streamRagAnswer (async generator)
    API -> G: generate tokens (RAG completion)
    G --> API: token chunk
    API --> B: event: **token** { token }
  end

  opt critiqueAnswer + correctAnswer
    API -> G: critique then optional correct
    API --> B: event: **correction** (if materially different)
  end

  API --> B: event: **done**
  API -> API: res.end()
end

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/search.ts** (~154+),
  **queryOptimizer**, **reranker**, **ragCompletion**,
  **feedbackMemory**, **ragEvaluation**.
  Client must parse **SSE** events.
end note

@enduml
